Dappled sunlight through the trees casts shadows at the Tsutaya Book store in Daikanyama, Tokyo.
</p>

<p class="jp">
代官山の蔦屋書店に木漏れ日が差し込み、影を落とす。
 </p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tokyo" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Dappled sunlight through the trees casts shadows at the Tsutaya Book store in Daikanyama, Tokyo.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2410_A7R06810.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2410_A7R06810.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Nagoya Castle・名古屋城</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241010/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Nagoya Castle・名古屋城" /><published>2024-10-10T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-10-10T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/nagoya</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241010/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Nagoya Castle's main tower keep in the afternoon sun.
</p>

<p class="jp">
午後の日差しに照らされた名古屋城天守閣の眺め。
 </p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Japan" /><category term="Castles" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Nagoya Castle's main tower keep in the afternoon sun.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2410_A7R06717.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2410_A7R06717.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Inuyama Castle・犬山城</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241009/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Inuyama Castle・犬山城" /><published>2024-10-09T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-10-09T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/inuyama</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241009/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
A boat on the Kiso River near Inuyama Castle and Mt. Igiyama, at dusk.
</p>

<p class="jp">
夕暮れの犬山城近くの木曽川に浮かぶ一艘の船。伊木山が背景に見える。
 </p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Japan" /><category term="Castles" /><category term="Rivers" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Boats" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A boat on the Kiso River near Inuyama Castle and Mt. Igiyama, at dusk.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2410_A7R06785_ai-3.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2410_A7R06785_ai-3.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>